{"tid":166102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[做乜鳩?] 隨街問人拎嘢食 尖嘴男反被毆兼搶錢","createTime":"2017-03-22T00:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T01:11:07.000Z","uid":28435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3cc01259d1e1a18b34746ec976e9400b2e88475","tid":166102,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:32:39.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】尖沙嘴漆咸道南100號香港歷史博物館對開，昨凌晨5時許，一名32歲印度男子，向兩名正在聊天同鄉索取食物，稍後與同鄉發生爭執，遭對方持皮帶鞭打及木棍毆打，事主不敵頭及左眼受傷，身上一個內有2千多元現金的袋被人搶走，混亂間其iPhone手機墮地，亦被惡漢撿走，損失總值約1萬元。警員到場調查及兜截，將傷者送院治理，案件則列傷人處理。"},{"pid":"912708f7a8c187c5d65700283e38c652c9612351","tid":166102,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:33:47.000Z","msg":"SM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c909cabbe9648f1fd4c2d90e435cb1d5b8c623","tid":166102,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:41:43.000Z","msg":"條友都唔係窮啦 而家得不償失喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1aff5b91e8c8a56189d1e1d4c5e69de1fb3b50","tid":166102,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:43:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54ce67d998d9feedcbc9bbd850ce4df72bc89298","tid":166102,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T01:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友都唔係窮啦 而家得不償失喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢up 既姐 佢話比人搶左幾億都得架啦"}]}